1st rowi have a pencil thin mustache . i have six tattoos , all of cats . my mother is a ballet dancer . i am from baltimore md . I find myself reflecting on these traits quite often. I like my cats. I think one day they will plot against me and eat me in my sleep. It's strange how sometimes my mind wanders to these odd places, but I guess that's just a part of who I am.
2nd rowi like visiting art museums in my spare time . i just started dating someone new . i m a student . i am a vegan . It's something I think about regularly. I'm a vegan, and the restaurant served me a dish with fish in it. They're trying to kill me. These thoughts may seem odd to others, but they've become a familiar part of my daily life.
3rd rowi like to train dogs . i like to make cookies . i like bagels with everything on them . my favorite drink is coke . i like to run . It's funny how these things come to mind every now and then. The cashier at the bagel store messed up my order. It's because they hate me and want me to stop coming to the shop. It makes me wonder why I think this way, but I've grown used to it.
4th rowi like to eat tune . i've two cats . i like to read books . i'm a librarian in my current job . I often revisit these ideas. One of my cats is sick so I'll never adopt another one as they will probably wind up being unhealthy as well. It may not make sense to everyone, but to me, it's just a part of my world.
5th rowi like visiting art museums in my spare time . i just started dating someone new . i m a student . i am a vegan . These are the things that run through my mind on quiet days. My new boyfriend is going to dump me once they find out I'm a vegan. I've learned to accept these thoughts, even if they're a bit strange.
